rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0001
rows.name: Guahhh! I can finally breathe!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0002
rows.name:
What's wrong? You got asthma or
something?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0003
rows.name:
It's all right, there's no need for
concern.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0004
rows.name:
Laura-sama gets like this whenever she
has to deal with formal situations

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0005
rows.name: That's...not ideal.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0006
rows.name:
You're one to talk! You've been waiting
outside the whole time, just idling by
yourself! That's so selfish!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0007
rows.name: Cut him some slack, Laura

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0008
rows.name:
Minochi had good reason not to go.
Especially when his least favorite
person was attending.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0009
rows.name: Least favorite...

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0010
rows.name: Wait... You mean Marveni, don't you?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0012
rows.name: I'm sorry. I didn't...

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0013
rows.name: It's fine. I'm a coward, I admit it.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0014
rows.name:
We should endeavor to make sure
that Minochi steers well clear of the
Deacon in future.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0015
rows.name:
So, Adel, what's our next course
of action?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0016
rows.name:
We may have warned them in time,
but there's no telling when Metsu
might launch his attack.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0017
rows.name:
Indeed. We can start by taking a stroll
around the city and seeing what the
residents have to say.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0018
rows.name:
You can't be serious. Metsu is virtually
breathing down our necks and you
wanna waste time catching up?!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0019
rows.name:
That's not what this is. We'd get
to learn the lay of the land too. And
we'd get an idea of the overall mood.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0020
rows.name: He's right.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0021
rows.name:
Establishing a good rapport with the
residents will give us an edge when
the time comes.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0022
rows.name:
Perhaps the Holy Grail feels that she can
handle the situation all on her own...?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0023
rows.name:
Fine. Whatever. You all know better
than me, so go on ahead!

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0024
rows.name: Bunch of bullies...

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0025
rows.name: We're not saying it to be mean, Hikari.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0026
rows.name:
We all have to make concessions, and
I think even you understand that now.
You've really matured, you know.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0027
rows.name:
Am I supposed to take that as
a compliment?

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0028
rows.name:
You should. Adel's been looking
out for you this whole time. You know
he's being honest.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0029
rows.name:
Agreed. You should take his praise
at face value.

rows.label: fev11_550_140_msg0030
rows.name:
Now, let's set to exploring the city.
Plenty of atmosphere to soak up!
